WARNING:  run_seminaive_inner: seed compile error: variable predicate in rule body not supported
WARNING:  run_seminaive_inner: seed compile error: variable predicate in rule body not supported
WARNING:  run_seminaive_inner: seed compile error: variable predicate in rule body not supported
